WEBVTT

1.1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.124
Price with total confidence — because everything about Magppie pricing is fixed, transparent, and defensible.

2.1
00:00:09.124 --> 00:00:16.021
Wellness Kitchens: eighty-four hundred to ten thousand eight hundred rupees per square foot, by finish.

2.2
00:00:16.021 --> 00:00:22.919
Wellness Wardrobes: seven thousand three hundred twenty.

2.3
00:00:22.919 --> 00:00:29.816
A typical ten-by-ten kitchen: twelve to fifteen lakhs, excluding accessories, appliances, and GST.

3.1
00:00:29.816 --> 00:00:36.615
Included: SilverStone cabinets and shutters, internal shelves, soft-close hardware, factory fabrication, transport, and installation.

3.2
00:00:36.615 --> 00:00:43.414
Quoted separately: accessories, appliances, premium upgrades.

3.3
00:00:43.414 --> 00:00:50.213
And the customer's scope — electrical, plumbing, civil — goes into a written scope matrix before confirmation.

3.4
00:00:50.213 --> 00:00:57.012
No surprises.

4.1
00:00:57.012 --> 00:01:01.567
The guarantees do the selling: twenty-five years, unconditional, on the stone.

4.2
00:01:01.567 --> 00:01:06.122
Ten years on hardware.

4.3
00:01:06.122 --> 00:01:10.677
Two on lighting.

4.4
00:01:10.677 --> 00:01:15.232
And twenty-five complimentary annual services — deep cleaning, sanitisation, alignment.

5.1
00:01:15.232 --> 00:01:22.313
When price pressure comes, anchor it: wood material under one hundred rupees a square foot.

5.2
00:01:22.313 --> 00:01:29.395
SilverStone, around five hundred.

5.3
00:01:29.395 --> 00:01:36.476
A Magppie kitchen, eighty-four hundred to ten-eight all-inclusive — while a branded wood kitchen costs about the same and brings toxins and maintenance with it.

6.1
00:01:36.476 --> 00:01:44.518
On payment milestones: the schedule starts with a fifty percent advance, and your wellness consultant confirms the full schedule during the design phase.

6.2
00:01:44.518 --> 00:01:52.560
Do not quote a full split from memory — the standard is under review.

7.1
00:01:52.560 --> 00:01:59.698
Your pricing notes.

7.2
00:01:59.698 --> 00:02:06.837
One — kitchens eighty-four hundred to ten-eight per square foot; wardrobes seven thousand three hundred twenty; a ten-by-ten kitchen, twelve to fifteen lakhs.

7.3
00:02:06.837 --> 00:02:13.975
Two — guarantees: twenty-five years on stone, ten on hardware, two on lighting, and twenty-five annual services.

7.4
00:02:13.975 --> 00:02:21.114
Three — never cheap, discount, or negotiate.

7.5
00:02:21.114 --> 00:02:28.252
Four — on the payment split, only the fifty percent advance is common ground; the consultant confirms the rest during design.

8.1
00:02:28.252 --> 00:02:31.019
Fixed price.

8.2
00:02:31.019 --> 00:02:33.786
Complete transparency.

8.3
00:02:33.786 --> 00:02:36.553
Never the words cheap, discount, or negotiate.

8.4
00:02:36.553 --> 00:02:39.320
Quiz time.

